reviews.title: Adorable......as usual :)
reviews.comment: So pretty, so cute!  As for lying.....that\'s not true :(  This dev always lets you try his/her work so that you can decide whether or not you want to buy it.  I think that\'s very considerate.  It\'s a courtesy......not a lie!  Read what\'s written before accusing someone!  Again, nice work dev!  Another  winner.  Love your work.....and thanks for letting me try this first :)
